# Figment release artifact SHA256 checksums.
#
# Format: <sha256>  <filename>
# Lookup is by the on-disk basename of each downloaded file. Lines starting
# with `#` are ignored.
#
# Entries marked `# PENDING` have not been recorded yet. BuildYourOwn.sh will
# log a warning and continue when the lookup returns no hash, so the file is
# safe to ship in this incomplete state. Populate before tagging v1.0.0:
#
#   sha256sum \
#     /tmp/figment-build.*/llama-b8893-bin-ubuntu-x64.tar.gz \
#     /tmp/figment-build.*/llama-b8893-bin-ubuntu-vulkan-x64.tar.gz \
#     /path/to/usb/.system/mlabonne_Qwen3-4B-abliterated-Q8_0.gguf \
#     ...
#
# To bypass verification entirely (e.g. when overriding URLs):
#   FIGMENT_SKIP_CHECKSUMS=1 ./BuildYourOwn.sh ...
# To point at a different checksum file:
#   FIGMENT_CHECKSUMS_FILE=/path/to/file.sha256 ./BuildYourOwn.sh ...

# Runtime tarballs (ggml-org/llama.cpp release b8893)
# PENDING  llama-b8893-bin-ubuntu-x64.tar.gz
# PENDING  llama-b8893-bin-ubuntu-arm64.tar.gz
# PENDING  llama-b8893-bin-ubuntu-vulkan-x64.tar.gz
# PENDING  llama-b8893-bin-ubuntu-vulkan-arm64.tar.gz

